{
  "id": 71,
  "nameSimple": "Nuh",
  "nameArabic": "نوح",
  "versesCount": 28,
  "revelationPlace": "makkah",
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 5420,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "verseKey": "71:1",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": " إِنَّآ أَرْسَلْنَا نُوحًا إِلَىٰ قَوْمِهِۦٓ أَنْ أَنذِرْ قَوْمَكَ مِن قَبْلِ أَن يَأْتِيَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌ",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101276,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, We sent Noah to his people, [saying], \"Warn your people before there comes to them a painful punishment.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752133,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已派谴努哈去教化他的宗族，我说：“在痛苦的刑罚降临你的宗族之前，你当警告他们。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5421,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "verseKey": "71:2",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "قَالَ يَـٰقَوْمِ إِنِّى لَكُمْ نَذِيرٌ مُّبِينٌ",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101298,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He said, \"O my people, indeed I am to you a clear warner -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752134,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他说：我的宗族啊！我确是你们的坦率的警告者，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5422,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "verseKey": "71:3",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَنِ ٱعْبُدُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ وَٱتَّقُوهُ وَأَطِيعُونِ",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101321,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "To worship Allāh, fear Him and obey me.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752135,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你们应当崇拜安拉，应当敬畏他，应当服从我，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5423,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "verseKey": "71:4",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَغْفِرْ لَكُم مِّن ذُنُوبِكُمْ وَيُؤَخِّرْكُمْ إِلَىٰٓ أَجَلٍ مُّسَمًّى ۚ إِنَّ أَجَلَ ٱللَّهِ إِذَا جَآءَ لَا يُؤَخَّرُ ۖ لَوْ كُنتُمْ تَعْلَمُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101333,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He [i.e., Allāh] will forgive you of your sins and delay you for a specified term. Indeed, the time [set by] Allāh, when it comes, will not be delayed, if you only knew.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752136,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他就赦宥你们的罪过，并且让你们延迟到一个定期。安拉的定期一旦来临的时候，是绝不延迟的，假若你们知道。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5424,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "verseKey": "71:5",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "قَالَ رَبِّ إِنِّى دَعَوْتُ قَوْمِى لَيْلًا وَنَهَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101345,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He said, \"My Lord, indeed I invited my people [to truth] night and day.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752137,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他说：“我的主啊！我确已日夜召唤我的宗族，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5425,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "verseKey": "71:6",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَلَمْ يَزِدْهُمْ دُعَآءِىٓ إِلَّا فِرَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101356,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But my invitation increased them not except in flight [i.e., aversion].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752138,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "但我的召唤使他们愈加逃避。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5426,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "verseKey": "71:7",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَإِنِّى كُلَّمَا دَعَوْتُهُمْ لِتَغْفِرَ لَهُمْ جَعَلُوٓا۟ أَصَـٰبِعَهُمْ فِىٓ ءَاذَانِهِمْ وَٱسْتَغْشَوْا۟ ثِيَابَهُمْ وَأَصَرُّوا۟ وَٱسْتَكْبَرُوا۟ ٱسْتِكْبَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101368,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And indeed, every time I invited them that You may forgive them, they put their fingers in their ears, covered themselves with their garments,<sup foot_note=230164>1</sup> persisted, and were arrogant with [great] arrogance.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752139,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我每次召唤他们来受你的赦宥的时候，他们总是以指头塞住他们的耳朵，以衣服蒙住他们的头，他们固执而自大。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5427,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "verseKey": "71:8",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ إِنِّى دَعَوْتُهُمْ جِهَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101383,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then I invited them publicly.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752140,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后我大声召唤他们，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5428,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "verseKey": "71:9",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ إِنِّىٓ أَعْلَنتُ لَهُمْ وَأَسْرَرْتُ لَهُمْ إِسْرَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101395,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then I announced to them and [also] confided to them secretly",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752141,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后我公开地训导他们，秘密地劝谏他们，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5429,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "verseKey": "71:10",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَقُلْتُ ٱسْتَغْفِرُوا۟ رَبَّكُمْ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ غَفَّارًا",
      "pageNumber": 570,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101278,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And said, 'Ask forgiveness of your Lord. Indeed, He is ever a Perpetual Forgiver.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752142,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我说，你们应当向你们的主求饶--他确是至赦的--",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5430,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "verseKey": "71:11",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يُرْسِلِ ٱلسَّمَآءَ عَلَيْكُم مِّدْرَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101280,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He will send [rain from] the sky upon you in [continuing] showers",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752143,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他就使丰足的雨水降临你们，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5431,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "verseKey": "71:12",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَيُمْدِدْكُم بِأَمْوَٰلٍ وَبَنِينَ وَيَجْعَل لَّكُمْ جَنَّـٰتٍ وَيَجْعَل لَّكُمْ أَنْهَـٰرًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101282,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And give you increase in wealth and children and provide for you gardens and provide for you rivers.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752144,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "并且以财产和子嗣援助你们，为你们创造园圃和河流。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5432,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "verseKey": "71:13",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مَّا لَكُمْ لَا تَرْجُونَ لِلَّهِ وَقَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101284,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "What is [the matter] with you that you do not attribute to Allāh [due] grandeur",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752145,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你们怎么不希望安拉的尊重呢？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5433,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "verseKey": "71:14",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَقَدْ خَلَقَكُمْ أَطْوَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101286,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "While He has created you in stages?<sup foot_note=230167>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752146,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他确已经过几个阶段创造了你们。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5434,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "verseKey": "71:15",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَلَمْ تَرَوْا۟ كَيْفَ خَلَقَ ٱللَّهُ سَبْعَ سَمَـٰوَٰتٍ طِبَاقًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101288,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Do you not consider how Allāh has created seven heavens in layers<sup foot_note=230168>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752147,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "难道你们没有看到安拉怎样创造七层天，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5435,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "verseKey": "71:16",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَجَعَلَ ٱلْقَمَرَ فِيهِنَّ نُورًا وَجَعَلَ ٱلشَّمْسَ سِرَاجًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101290,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And made the moon therein a [reflected] light and made the sun a burning lamp?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752148,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "并以月亮为光明，以太阳为明灯吗？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5436,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "verseKey": "71:17",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱللَّهُ أَنۢبَتَكُم مِّنَ ٱلْأَرْضِ نَبَاتًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101292,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And Allāh has caused you to grow from the earth a [progressive] growth.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752149,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "安拉使你们从大地生长出来，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5437,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "verseKey": "71:18",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ يُعِيدُكُمْ فِيهَا وَيُخْرِجُكُمْ إِخْرَاجًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101294,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then He will return you into it and extract you [another] extraction.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752150,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后使你们再返于大地，然后，又把你们从大地取出来。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5438,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "verseKey": "71:19",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱللَّهُ جَعَلَ لَكُمُ ٱلْأَرْضَ بِسَاطًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101296,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And Allāh has made for you the earth an expanse",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752151,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "安拉为你们而平展大地，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5439,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "verseKey": "71:20",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 506,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "لِّتَسْلُكُوا۟ مِنْهَا سُبُلًا فِجَاجًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101300,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "That you may follow therein roads of passage.'\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752152,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "以便你们在大地上走着宽阔的道路。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5440,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "verseKey": "71:21",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 507,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "قَالَ نُوحٌ رَّبِّ إِنَّهُمْ عَصَوْنِى وَٱتَّبَعُوا۟ مَن لَّمْ يَزِدْهُ مَالُهُۥ وَوَلَدُهُۥٓ إِلَّا خَسَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101302,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Noah said, \"My Lord, indeed they have disobeyed me and followed him whose wealth and children will not increase him except in loss.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752153,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "努哈说：“我的主啊！他们确已违抗我，他们顺从那因财产和子嗣而更加亏折的人们，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5441,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "verseKey": "71:22",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 507,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمَكَرُوا۟ مَكْرًا كُبَّارًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101304,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And they conspired an immense conspiracy",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752154,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "那等人曾定了一个重大的计谋，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5442,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "verseKey": "71:23",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 507,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَقَالُوا۟ لَا تَذَرُنَّ ءَالِهَتَكُمْ وَلَا تَذَرُنَّ وَدًّا وَلَا سُوَاعًا وَلَا يَغُوثَ وَيَعُوقَ وَنَسْرًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101306,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And said, 'Never leave your gods and never leave Wadd or Suwāʿ or Yaghūth and Yaʿūq and Nasr.'<sup foot_note=230173>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752155,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们说：“你们绝不要放弃你们的众神明，你们绝不要放弃旺德、素佤尔、叶巫斯、叶欧格、奈斯尔。'",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5443,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "verseKey": "71:24",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 507,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَقَدْ أَضَلُّوا۟ كَثِيرًا ۖ وَلَا تَزِدِ ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ إِلَّا ضَلَـٰلًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101308,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And already they have misled many. And, [my Lord], do not increase the wrongdoers except in error.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752156,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们确已使许多人迷误，求你使不义的人们更加迷误。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5444,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "verseKey": "71:25",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 507,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مِّمَّا خَطِيٓـَٔـٰتِهِمْ أُغْرِقُوا۟ فَأُدْخِلُوا۟ نَارًا فَلَمْ يَجِدُوا۟ لَهُم مِّن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ أَنصَارًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101310,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Because of their sins they were drowned and put into the Fire, and they found not for themselves besides Allāh [any] helpers.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752157,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们因为自己的罪恶而被淹死，遂堕入火狱，故他们没有获得援助的人们来抵御安拉。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5445,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "verseKey": "71:26",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 507,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَقَالَ نُوحٌ رَّبِّ لَا تَذَرْ عَلَى ٱلْأَرْضِ مِنَ ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ دَيَّارًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101313,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And Noah said, \"My Lord, do not leave upon the earth from among the disbelievers an inhabitant.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752158,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "努哈说：“我的主啊！求你不要留一个不信道者在大地上，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5446,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "verseKey": "71:27",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 507,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّكَ إِن تَذَرْهُمْ يُضِلُّوا۟ عِبَادَكَ وَلَا يَلِدُوٓا۟ إِلَّا فَاجِرًا كَفَّارًا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101316,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, if You leave them, they will mislead Your servants and not beget except [every] wicked one and [confirmed] disbeliever.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752159,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "如果你留他们，他们将使你的众仆迷误，他们只生育不道德的、不感恩的子女。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5447,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "verseKey": "71:28",
      "hizbNumber": 57,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 228,
      "rukuNumber": 507,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "رَّبِّ ٱغْفِرْ لِى وَلِوَٰلِدَىَّ وَلِمَن دَخَلَ بَيْتِىَ مُؤْمِنًا وَلِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ وَٱلْمُؤْمِنَـٰتِ وَلَا تَزِدِ ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ إِلَّا تَبَارًۢا",
      "pageNumber": 571,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101318,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "My Lord, forgive me and my parents and whoever enters my house a believer and the believing men and believing women. And do not increase the wrongdoers except in destruction.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752160,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我的主啊！求你赦宥我和我的父母，赦宥信道而入我的房屋的人，以及信士们和信女们。求你使不义的人们更加毁灭。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}